<p>I was using <a href="https://github.com/720kb/angular-tooltips" rel="nofollow">this angularjs tooltip library</a> to show tooltips.</p>  <p>Here's my <strong>HTML:</strong> </p>  <pre><code>&lt;span tooltips tooltip-title="Recommenders" tooltip-show-trigger="click" tooltip-view="/static/templates/tooltips/recommenders.html" tooltip-view-ctrl="FeedCtrl"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Here's my <strong>tooltip partial:</strong></p>  <pre><code>&lt;div ng-repeat="recommender in recommenders_list"&gt;     {{recommender}} &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>  <p>The problem I am facing is that when I update the 'recommenders_list' array in my controller, the same is not reflected in the tooltip template. How can I update my tooltip partial?</p>